song.title: High Grounded
song.info:
From the music disk "blur plastiq", ftp://ftp.scene.org/mirrors/hornet/music/disks/1996/fm-plast.zip. Notes from Mellow-D:
Very much rougher than the rest of the stuff. I actually turn down the amplification in FT2 because this is a bit overdriven :). More filters in the leads.
Heh, do you hear that panning feedback thing? Me and Mig made that by plugging a mic into my effects processor, plugging that into his set of analog effects, and going (just once) "ha" into the microphone. No kidding. Wow.
This song has basically let off a lot of steam I had at the time.
